{"image_id": "CHD_2011_page_90", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "CHURCH & DWIGHT CO., INC. AND SUBSIDIARIES", "bbox": [383.3, 158.9, 891.8, 179.7]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS—(Continued)", "bbox": [298.1, 196.4, 977.0, 217.2]}, {"text": "U.S. Pension Plan Termination", "bbox": [183.3, 246.4, 444.4, 267.2]}, {"text": "On January 27, 2010, the Company’s Board of Directors approved the termination, effective April 15, 2010,", "bbox": [204.2, 281.9, 1108.0, 302.7]}, {"text": "of The Church & Dwight Co., Inc. Retirement Plan for Hourly Employees (the “U.S. Pension Plan”), under", "bbox": [162.5, 306.9, 1059.1, 327.7]}, {"text": "which approximately 766 participants, including 46 active employees, have accrued benefits. On December 1,", "bbox": [162.5, 331.9, 1082.2, 352.7]}, {"text": "2010, the Company as plan sponsor of the U.S. Pension Plan, purchased a non participating group annuity", "bbox": [162.5, 356.9, 1047.6, 377.7]}, {"text": "contract from the Principal Life Insurance Company for the benefit of certain former and current employees with", "bbox": [162.5, 381.9, 1106.3, 402.7]}, {"text": "vested benefits in, and retired participants currently receiving benefits from, the U.S. Pension Plan. In addition,", "bbox": [162.5, 406.9, 1090.6, 427.7]}, {"text": "effective December 1, 2010, an existing participating annuity contract with Aetna Insurance Company was", "bbox": [162.5, 431.9, 1054.4, 452.7]}, {"text": "changed to a non-participating annuity contract.", "bbox": [162.5, 456.9, 562.3, 477.7]}, {"text": "The purchase price of the contracts was approximately $63 million, which was funded from the assets of the", "bbox": [204.2, 502.5, 1108.3, 523.4]}, {"text": "U.S. Pension Plan on December 1, 2010 (considered the measurement date for accounting purposes) and a", "bbox": [162.5, 527.5, 1050.1, 548.4]}, {"text": "one-time payment by the Company of approximately $14 million ($9 million after taxes). The transactions", "bbox": [162.5, 552.5, 1052.2, 573.4]}, {"text": "resulted in the transfer and settlement of the U.S. pension benefit obligation, thus relieving the Company of any", "bbox": [162.5, 577.5, 1094.7, 598.4]}, {"text": "responsibility for the U.S. Pension Plan obligations.", "bbox": [162.5, 602.5, 595.3, 623.4]}, {"text": "As a result of the transfer of the U.S. Pension Plan obligations and assets described above, the Company", "bbox": [204.2, 648.2, 1074.6, 669.0]}, {"text": "recorded a charge to earnings in the fourth quarter of 2010 of approximately $24 million pre-tax or $0.11 per", "bbox": [162.5, 673.2, 1071.9, 694.0]}, {"text": "share. This charge is included in selling, general and administrative expenses.", "bbox": [162.5, 698.2, 811.1, 719.0]}, {"text": "The following table provides information on the status of the defined benefit plans at December 31:", "bbox": [204.2, 743.8, 1036.0, 764.6]}, {"text": "Pension Plans", "bbox": [831.8, 787.0, 930.4, 803.7]}, {"text": "Nonpension", "bbox": [995.7, 770.3, 1080.0, 787.0]}, {"text": "Postretirement Plans", "bbox": [963.3, 787.0, 1112.7, 803.7]}, {"text": "(In millions)", "bbox": [162.5, 812.0, 250.0, 828.7]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [825.8, 812.0, 859.2, 828.7]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [902.9, 812.0, 936.2, 828.7]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [981.4, 812.0, 1014.7, 828.7]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [1061.1, 812.0, 1094.5, 828.7]}, {"text": "Change in Benefit Obligation:", "bbox": [162.5, 838.2, 414.4, 859.0]}, {"text": "Benefit obligation at beginning of year . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [204.2, 859.0, 798.8, 879.8]}, {"text": "$ 81.2", "bbox": [815.6, 858.8, 869.5, 879.6]}, {"text": "$129.8", "bbox": [890.9, 859.0, 948.2, 879.8]}, {"text": "$ 24.3", "bbox": [971.1, 858.8, 1025.0, 879.6]}, {"text": "$ 22.3", "bbox": [1050.9, 859.0, 1104.8, 879.8]}, {"text": "Service cost . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [204.2, 879.8, 